VULNERABILITY OVERVIEW

CLEARTEXT STORAGE OF SENSITIVE INFORMATIONCWE-312: Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information, http://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/312.html, web site last accessed October 20, 2015.

The eWebServer stores passwords in cleartext.
